**Story**
Once, Upon a time, In a forest, there lived a monke who resided on a berry tree , Which was on the banks of a river. In the same forest,there lived a crocodile and his wife

The Monke wanted to make a cloth for himself using crocodile skin. He slowly started to try and befriend the crocodile by feeeding the berries. THe berries were delicious and the crocodile liked them.
After some time,The monkey started poisoning the berries...